short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Turns instances of 'cash' and 'money' into 'cash money'

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: CashMoney is a simple extension that takes any instances of the words "cash" or "money" on a page and changes them to "cash money," except for when the phrase "cash money" is already being used.
